{
  "uid": "v12-0-scenes-vars",
  "title": "Grafana 12.0 — Scenes Chained Variables",
  "description": "Scenes is the mandatory dashboard runtime as of 12.0. This demo shows Scenes' chained-variable evaluation — `$job` drives `$instance` drives the panel queries, all re-rendering reactively.",
  "tags": ["grafana-12", "v12.0", "scenes", "variables", "v12-demo"],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {"from": "now-15m", "to": "now"},
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {"list": [
    {"name": "ds_prom", "type": "datasource", "query": "prometheus", "refresh": 1, "current": {"text": "Prometheus", "value": "prom"}},
    {"name": "job", "type": "query", "label": "Job", "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"}, "query": {"query": "label_values(up, job)", "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"}, "refresh": 2, "multi": false, "current": {"text": "grafana", "value": "grafana"}, "hide": 0},
    {"name": "instance", "type": "query", "label": "Instance (chained on $job)", "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"}, "query": {"query": "label_values(up{job=\"$job\"}, instance)", "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"}, "refresh": 2, "multi": false, "hide": 0}
  ]},
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1, "type": "text", "title": "",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "### Scenes runtime (12.0)\n\nSwitch **Job** at the top — **Instance** re-populates automatically because Scenes re-evaluates every variable whose query references `$job`. Panel queries re-run only when their inputs change.\n\nThis is the declarative dataflow that `dashboardScene=true` enables. The flag is effectively mandatory in 12 and locked on in 13."}
    },
    {
      "id": 2, "type": "stat", "title": "up for `$job / $instance`",
      "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 4},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "expr": "up{job=\"$job\", instance=\"$instance\"}"}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"mappings": [{"type": "value", "options": {"0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"}, "1": {"text": "UP", "color": "green"}}}], "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red", "value": null}, {"color": "green", "value": 1}]}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 3, "type": "timeseries", "title": "scrape_duration_seconds — `$job`",
      "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 16, "x": 8, "y": 4},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "expr": "scrape_duration_seconds{job=\"$job\"}", "legendFormat": "{{instance}}"}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s", "decimals": 4, "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []},
      "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "calcs": ["mean", "last"], "placement": "right"}}
    },
    {
      "id": 4, "type": "timeseries", "title": "scrape_samples_scraped — `$job / $instance`",
      "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 11},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "expr": "scrape_samples_scraped{job=\"$job\", instance=\"$instance\"}"}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 20}}, "overrides": []},
      "options": {"legend": {"showLegend": false}, "tooltip": {"mode": "single"}}
    }
  ]
}
